posts.name: pryland
posts.cooked:
Let’s Go Wago!   A pair of wire cutters/strippers + Wago - JST = hassle free CAN. 100% Wago in 2023. NO JST’s. Tons of hard hits 0 failures.  NOTE: we do use ferrules on the CAN wires.  A simple non scientific pull test using Wagos and bare wires vs  Wago’s and ferrules will prove that the ferrules make a huge difference.
